      "comment": "SHE LIKES BEER (1) turned in a fair 4th placed finish last time at this track over 500m (28.50). Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings three times from five attempts. Better than last start and worth following up. VINTAGE KING (7) was responsible for a modest effort most recently when fifth at Sandown over 595m behind Motor City Rossi (35.27) in a Grade 4/5. Cannot be taken lightly. KRIS BAR IMOGEN (8) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fifth (28.69) in a Grade 5 at this track. Has a good record here including three wins. Worth following up. DANCE LADY DANCE (2) is worth some thought after placing from the same draw last start.",
